sequenceDiagram
  participant A as Renderer A<br/>(login page)
  participant S as Storage Service
  participant B as Renderer B<br/>(dashboard)

  A->>A: setItem("access", x)<br/>cached map 갱신 (sync)
  A->>S: Mojo Put(access)
  A->>A: setItem("refresh", y)<br/>cached map 갱신 (sync)
  A->>S: Mojo Put(refresh)
  A->>A: window.location.replace
  Note over A: unload

  Note over B: 새 document 로드
  B->>S: Mojo GetAll()
  Note over S: race window 열림<br/>(이전 Put과 새 GetAll의<br/>처리 순서가 가변)
  S-->>B: 부분 상태<br/>(access nullish인 시나리오)

  Note over B: zustand persist<br/>hydration
  B->>B: setState({access:null, refresh:y})
  B->>S: Mojo Put(remove access)
  Note over S: if/else가 race 결과 영속화
